{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-211","title":"离职解雇","sectionId":"chapter-09","sectionTitle":"遇见职场“大红人”","pageStart":1047,"pageEnd":1051,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":24,"duplicateEntryCount":10,"pages":[{"number":1047,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"211 离职解雇"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"employee [ɪmˈplɔɪiː]","headword":"employee"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.受雇者，雇员"},{"type":"note","text":"◎employee turnover员工流动"},{"type":"entry","text":"quit office 辞职","headword":"quit office"},{"type":"entry","text":"resignation letter 辞职信","headword":"resignation letter"},{"type":"entry","text":"apply for resignation 申请辞职","headword":"apply for resignation"},{"type":"entry","text":"hand over 移交","headword":"hand over"},{"type":"entry","text":"relevant document 相关文件","headword":"relevant document"}]},{"number":1048,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"hand in 上交","headword":"hand in"},{"type":"entry","text":"name plate 工牌","headword":"name plate"},{"type":"entry","text":"layoff [ˈleɪɒf]","headword":"layoff"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.解雇；裁员"},{"type":"note","text":"◎mass layoff大规模裁员"},{"type":"entry","text":"dismissal [dɪsˈmɪsl]","headword":"dismissal"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.解雇，免职；遣散"},{"type":"note","text":"◎unfair dismissal不公平解雇"},{"type":"entry","text":"sack [sæk]","headword":"sack"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.解雇"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.（俚语）解雇"},{"type":"entry","text":"rundown [ˈrʌndaʊn]","headword":"rundown"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.削减"}]},{"number":1049,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"staff cut 裁员","headword":"staff cut"},{"type":"entry","text":"poor management 经营不善","headword":"poor management"},{"type":"entry","text":"trammel [ˈtræml]","headword":"trammel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v.束缚，妨碍"},{"type":"entry","text":"slack in one's work 消极怠工","headword":"slack in one's work"},{"type":"entry","text":"absent from work 旷工","headword":"absent from work"},{"type":"entry","text":"get fired 被炒鱿鱼","headword":"get fired"},{"type":"entry","text":"out of work 失业","headword":"out of work"},{"type":"entry","text":"unemployment [ˌʌnɪmˈplɔɪmənt]","headword":"unemployment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.失业；失业率"},{"type":"note","text":"◎unemployment compensation失业补偿金"},{"type":"entry","text":"unemployment pension 失业津贴","headword":"unemployment pension"}]},{"number":1050,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"unemployment insurance 失业保险","headword":"unemployment insurance"},{"type":"entry","text":"inhumane [ˌɪnhjuːˈmeɪn]","headword":"inhumane"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.不近人情的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎inhumane treatment不人道的对待"},{"type":"entry","text":"turn livid with rage 气得脸色发青","headword":"turn livid with rage"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Why did you quit your job? （你为什么辞掉了工作？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I quit because I want to try something different. （我辞职是因为"},{"type":"text","text":"我想尝试不一样的工作。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I handed in my resignation letter. （我提交了辞职信。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Why? I can't understand. （为什么？我不能理解。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Your position is being made redundant. （你的职位被取消"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"}]},{"number":1051,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"B：I see. So where do I go from here?（明白了。那我要去哪儿"},{"type":"text","text":"呢？）"}]}]}